#
msgid ""
msgstr ""

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_INTRO_NAME"
msgstr "Dẫn Nhập"

#. world_info.csv: 这是一个诸多修士竞相修行的修仙世界。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_INTRO_DESC"
msgstr "Thế gian này là Tu Tiên Giới, vạn tộc tranh hùng."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_REALM_NAME"
msgstr "Cảnh Giới"

#. world_info.csv: 修仙的境界从弱到强：练气、筑基、金丹、元婴。每个境界分前期、中期、后期。境界间差距很大。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_REALM_DESC"
msgstr "Luận Giải Cảnh Giới Thiên Địa"
"Cultivation realms from weak to strong: Qi Refinement, Foundation "
"Establishment, Core Formation, Nascent Soul. Each realm is divided into "
"Early, Middle, and Late stages. The gap between realms is huge."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_LIFESPAN_NAME"
msgstr "Thọ Nguyên"

#. world_info.csv: 每个角色均有寿元上限。在大限将至的前20年身体会逐渐衰弱，有几率老死；一旦达到或超过寿元上限，...
msgid "WORLD_INFO_LIFESPAN_DESC"
msgstr "Thọ Nguyên Diễn Giải"
"Every character has a lifespan limit. The body will gradually weaken in the "
"20 years before the limit, with a chance of dying of old age; once the limit"
" is reached or exceeded, death is certain. Raising the realm and certain "
"treasures/elixirs can increase the lifespan limit."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_DEATH_NAME"
msgstr "Tử Vong"

#. world_info.csv: HP降至0以下也会死亡。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_DEATH_DESC"
msgstr "Sinh lực suy kiệt dưới số không, thân thể tất yếu hóa thành hư vô."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_REGION_NAME"
msgstr "Địa Vực"

#. world_info.csv: 不同区域有不同效果，在适当的区域做适当的事情事半功倍。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_REGION_DESC"
msgstr "Địa Vực Diễn Luận"
"Different regions have different effects; doing the right thing in the right"
" region yields twice the result with half the effort."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_CULTIVATION_NAME"
msgstr "Tu Luyện"

#. world_info.csv: 修炼可以增加经验，直到到达突破前的瓶颈。突破是概率事件，突破后会进入下一个境界。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_CULTIVATION_DESC"
msgstr "Tu Đạo Diễn Luận"
"Cultivation increases experience until reaching the bottleneck before "
"breakthrough. Breakthrough is a probability event; upon success, one enters "
"the next realm."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ROOT_NAME"
msgstr "Linh Căn"

#. world_info.csv: 灵根由五行元素（金、木、水、火、土）组成，分为单灵根、双灵根和天灵根。五行相克：金克木，木克土...
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ROOT_DESC"
msgstr "Căn Cơ Chân Giải"
"Spirit roots are composed of five elements (Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, "
"Earth), divided into Single, Dual, and Heavenly Spirit Roots. Five elements "
"interaction: Metal overcomes Wood, Wood overcomes Earth, Earth overcomes "
"Water, Water overcomes Fire, Fire overcomes Metal. Heavenly Spirit Root "
"contains all five elements and has an extra bonus during breakthrough. "
"Cultivation efficiency is highest in regions matching one's own spirit root "
"attribute."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_WORLD_QI_NAME"
msgstr "Thiên Địa Linh Khí"

#. world_info.csv: 世界每隔数年会有一次天象变动（如灵气潮汐），影响角色能力。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_WORLD_QI_DESC"
msgstr "Thiên Địa Linh Khí Luận"
"The world undergoes celestial changes (such as Qi Tides) every few years, "
"affecting character abilities."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SPIRIT_STONE_NAME"
msgstr "Linh Thạch"

#. world_info.csv: 修仙界的通用货币。可用于购买法宝丹药，通过采集、交易或掠夺获取。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SPIRIT_STONE_DESC"
msgstr "Linh Thạch Chân Giải"
"The common currency of the cultivation world. Can be used to buy artifacts "
"and elixirs, obtained through gathering, trading, or plundering."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SECT_NAME"
msgstr "Tông Môn"

#. world_info.csv: 修士的庇护所。加入宗门可习得独门功法、获同门庇护；散修自由但资源匮乏。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SECT_DESC"
msgstr "Tông Môn Diễn Luận"
"A shelter for cultivators. Joining a sect allows learning unique techniques "
"and gaining protection from fellow disciples; rogue cultivators are free but"
" lack resources."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_BATTLE_NAME"
msgstr "Giao Phong"

#. world_info.csv: 弱肉强食，境界压制极大，高境界者对低境界者有绝对优势。若对方死亡，胜者可掠夺败者财物。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_BATTLE_DESC"
msgstr "Chiến Đạo Diễn Luận"
"Survival of the fittest; realm suppression is huge, high-realm cultivators "
"have an absolute advantage over low-realm ones. If the opponent dies, the "
"winner can plunder the loser's belongings."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ACTION_NAME"
msgstr "Hành Động"

#. world_info.csv: 你有一系列可以执行的动作。要注意动作的效果、限制条件、区域和时间。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ACTION_DESC"
msgstr "Diễn Giải Biến Cố Tu Chân Giới"
"You have a series of executable actions. Pay attention to the effects, "
"restrictions, regions, and time of actions."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_EQUIPMENT_AND_ELIXIR_NAME"
msgstr "Pháp Bảo & Linh Đan"

#. world_info.csv: 通过兵器、辅助装备、丹药等装备，可以获得额外的属性加成，获得或小或大的增益。拥有好的装备或者服...
msgid "WORLD_INFO_EQUIPMENT_AND_ELIXIR_DESC"
msgstr "Tường Giải Pháp Bảo & Linh Đan Dược"
"Through weapons, auxiliary equipment, elixirs, etc., you can gain extra "
"attribute bonuses and small or large buffs. Owning good equipment or taking "
"good elixirs can bring great benefits."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SHOPPING_NAME"
msgstr "Thương Thành"

#. world_info.csv: 在城市区域可以购买练气级别丹药、兵器。购买丹药后会立刻服用强化自身。购买兵器可以帮自己切换兵器...
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SHOPPING_DESC"
msgstr "Phường Thị Giao Dịch"
"In city regions, you can buy Qi Refinement level elixirs and weapons. Buying"
" elixirs will immediately consume them to strengthen yourself. Buying "
"weapons can help you switch your weapon type to a handy one."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_AUCTION_NAME"
msgstr "Đấu Giá"

#. world_info.csv: 每隔一段不确定的时间会有神秘人组织的拍卖会，或许有好货出售。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_AUCTION_DESC"
msgstr "Đại Hội Đấu Giá"
"Every uncertain period of time, there will be an auction organized by a "
"mysterious person, perhaps selling good goods."

#. world_info.csv:
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SECRET_REALM_NAME"
msgstr "Bí Cảnh"

#. world_info.csv: 每隔数年会有秘境开启。进入秘境可能遭遇凶险，也可能获得高阶法宝和功法。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_SECRET_REALM_DESC"
msgstr "Tường Giải Bí Cảnh"
"Secret realms open every few years. Entering a secret realm may encounter "
"danger, but may also obtain high-level artifacts and techniques."

#. world_info.csv: 道统
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ORTHODOXY_NAME"
msgstr "Chính Đạo"

#. world_info.csv: 道、佛、儒等根本理念，决定门牌的根脚与修行起源。
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ORTHODOXY_DESC"
msgstr "Chính Đạo Chân Truyền"
"Different orthodoxies have different cultivation methods. Taoists respire, "
"Martial Artists temper their bodies, Buddhists meditate, and Confucians "
"educate the people."

#. world_info.csv: 道统
msgid "WORLD_INFO_ORTHODOXY_TITLE"
msgstr "Chính Đạo"
